<!--<h4><hi rend="italic">North and west faces.</hi></h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="1"/>sidhi gaṇeśayanamaḥ saṁvat 1459 <g type="ddanda">.</g> sā
<lb n="2" break="no"/>ke <g type="ddanda">.</g> 1325 <g type="ddanda">.</g> samaye <g type="ddanda">.</g> sarvadhārī nāma sa
<lb n="3" break="no"/>vatsere <g type="ddanda">.</g> paṭaṇaurakaṭake <g type="ddanda">.</g> vyāsa<unclear>u</unclear>
<lb n="4" break="no"/>pādhyā<supplied reason="omitted">ya</supplied>ko paṇati <g type="ddanda">.</g> visṇudāsaupā
<lb n="5" break="no"/><supplied reason="omitted">dhyā</supplied>ko nāti <g type="ddanda">.</g> paigu Upādhyāko putraḥ <g type="ddanda">.</g>
<lb n="6"/>kaliṁga vyāpārī laḍauusuratāṇa
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ko bhāī <g type="ddanda">.</g> riṣidāsa kurmakṣetra Ākhaṁ 
<lb n="8" break="no"/>ḍa dipa data ghoḍāvaṇijārā riṣīdā
<lb n="9" break="no"/>sanāyeka <g type="ddanda">.</g> śrī kurmanātha<unclear>ca</unclear>raṇaśara
<lb n="10" break="no"/><supplied reason="omitted">ṇa</supplied> śrīnarasihacaraṇaśaraṇaḥ <g type="ddanda">.</g> śubhaṁ
<lb n="11" break="no"/>mastuḥ <g type="ddanda">.</g>
</p>

<!--<h4><hi rend="italic">West face.</hi></h4>-->

<p>
<lb n="12"/>dirardhāsi gopālabhoi pallabhoi dvika
<lb n="13" break="no"/>ra gocare dilakeli śatā 100 <g type="ddanda">.</g> yethakī
<lb n="14"/>nītyādavā ghī Āḍa lekhai varsakai cāra
<lb n="15"/>puṭi daśamāṇa E hi lekha prati srahī
<lb n="16"/>kurmmanātha deva praśa karīvā <g type="ddanda">.</g> E <unclear>dha</unclear>rmma tī
<lb n="17" break="no"/>rupati śrīvaiṣṇavarakṣa [<g type="ddanda">.</g>]<note n="428-1">The figure of a horse is engraved here.</note>
</p>

